# ── Dev screenshots / verification artifacts ────────
# (kept out of the repo; remove these rules if you want them tracked)
/*.png
frontend/screenshots/
# 예외: README 미리보기용 화면 이미지(목 데이터·집계만 — 개별 업체/공고명·PII 없음)는 추적한다.
!docs/screenshots/*.png

# ── Business / strategy docs (kept LOCAL only — not for public repo) ──
